        "content": "> One guided tour option is to do Bana Hills + Golden bridge combo tour from Da Nang which will cost you $48 USD on Klook. This includes Ba Na Hills and Fantasy Park entrance tickets, Cable car ticket, English guide and pick-up and drop-off from Danang center.\n\nHow to book the tickets of Bana Hills for cheap directly from official source:\n\n Phone: (+84) 905 766 777\n Ticket booking Website: \n Daily cable car Timings: 07:30 - 21:00\n\nTo give you a quick overview, we have created a table below of the complete 2026 Ticket & Services Price List for Sun World Bana Hills, as published on the official site (You may verify from the link).\n\n## 1. Cable Car Tickets & Combos [...] Bana Hills + Buffet Ticket\n\n+ Adult: About 1,250,000 VND (Approx 48 USD)\n+ Child: Around 950,000 VND (Approx 37 USD)  \n    \n  This includes admission price with a buffet meal, suitable for visitors intending to tour and dine in the park the whole day. Not all restaurants are included and you can eat at the selected restaurants mentioned in your ticket.\n\n Night Admission Ticket:\n\n+ Adults: 1,000,000 VND (Approx 40 USD)\n+ Children (1-1.4m): 800,000 VND (Approx 30 USD)  \n    \n  These are night tickets that grant access from 3:00 PM to 10:00 PM and are less crowded; one can feel the unique atmosphere of nighttime. The ticket price includes a round-trip cable car ride, access to the Da Nang Golden Bridge, and a buffet dinner, but excludes Fantasy Park and the Wax Museum. [...] Mini tip: Book 2 to 3 days ahead on weekends and Tet holidays.\n6. Do you have family or group discounts?  \n   Currently, no official group or family discounts are made, but the combo tickets which include meal and transport tickets are a money saver for families.\n7. How much time should I devote to Ba Na Hills?  \n   Major sights can be seen in one full day, about 6 to 8 hours of photo shooting and Fantasy Park, together with the Danang Golden Bridge. Ba Na Hills day trip is a must do thing